    <item>
      <title>政策重点转向 卢比将继续跌至新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/rupee-set-to-keep-tiptoeing-to-new-lows-as-policy-pivot-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度卢比从今年年初新兴亚洲表现最好的货币跌至本季度表现最差的货币之一，而且跌势可能还会持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/rupee-set-to-keep-tiptoeing-to-new-lows-as-policy-pivot-in-focus</guid>
